		 tv_grab_dvb 0.10 Released ??/??/2007
==========================================================================
02/04/2007	Philipp Hahn	<pmhahn_pmhahn_de>		0.10
	* Add -i option for reading from file or custom demultiplex devices
	* Add -f option for writing to file instead of stdout
	* Support different character encodings
	* Translate 3 letter languages to 2 letter language IDs
	* Improved efficiency: Cache files in memory.

10/03/2008  Tero Pelander <tpeland_tkukoulu_fi>
    * Add -s option to make program silent
	* make the output obey xmltv.dtd 

